309
00:21:53,200 --> 00:21:55,100
Mais tu ne comprends pas...

310
00:21:56,000 --> 00:21:57,400
Maintenant?

311
00:21:57,700 --> 00:21:59,600
J'arrive.

312
00:22:00,800 --> 00:22:03,300
C'était un plaisir
de te parler, crétin.

